UE5 Blueprint File - BP_NPC_QuestComponent_v01
==============================================

This is a Blueprint Component that extends UQuestComponent (C++ class).

To create this blueprint in Unreal Engine 5.2+:
1. Right-click in Content Browser
2. Search for "UQuestComponent"
3. Select "BP_NPC_QuestComponent_v01"
4. Click "Create"

Components:
- AvailableQuestIDs (Array of FString)
- ActiveQuestIDs (Array of FString)
- CompletedQuestIDs (Array of FString)
- IsQuestGiver (Boolean)
- ReputationRequired (Float)
- ReputationGain (Float)
- ReputationLoss (Float)
- QuestMarker (Actor)
- QuestMarkerType (Enum: Arrow, Circle, Diamond, Star)
- QuestMarkerColor (LinearColor)
- QuestMarkerText (String)

Functions:
- InitializeQuests(TArray<FString>)
- GiveQuest(FString)
- UpdateQuestStep(FString, int32)
- CompleteQuest(FString)
- ShowQuestMarker()
- HideQuestMarker()
- CheckQuestProgress(FString) -> bool
- GiveQuestReward(FString)
- GetAvailableQuests() -> TArray<FString>
- GetActiveQuests() -> TArray<FString>
- GetCompletedQuests() -> TArray<FString>
- OnReputationChange(float)
- UpdateQuestMarkerVisibility()

Note: This blueprint must be compiled after adding components.
Note: This blueprint requires quest data assets from designers.
Note: This blueprint requires quest widget from UI designers.
Note: This blueprint requires quest marker actor from level designers.